name: eesubmit
body:
### Description
eesubmit makes it easier to submit your EE homework.

### Installation
1. Download the repository code
2. If you're on Mac, run `main/macInstall.bash`. If you're on Linux, run `main/linuxInstall.bash`

### Usage
1. move the pdf of your handwritten work into the same directory as your ipython notebook and name it "hwHand<x>.pdf" (where <x> is the hw assignment number)
2. execute the following command:
     `eesubmit`


### Authors and Contributors
Michael Snowden (@MichaelSnowden) and Dakota Sproch (@ddasnow)
